{"id":"265127909_Crossing_Minimization_for_1-page_and_2-page_Drawings_of_Graphs_with_Bounded_Treewidth","abstract":"We investigate crossing minimization for 1-page and 2-page book drawings. We\nshow that computing the 1-page crossing number is fixed-parameter tractable\nwith respect to the number of crossings, that testing 2-page planarity is\nfixed-parameter tractable with respect to treewidth, and that computing the\n2-page crossing number is fixed-parameter tractable with respect to the sum of\nthe number of crossings and the treewidth of the input graph. We prove these\nresults via Courcelle's theorem on the fixed-parameter tractability of\nproperties expressible in monadic second order logic for graphs of bounded\ntreewidth.","authors":["Michael J. Bannister","David Eppstein"],"meta":["August 2014","DOI:10.1007/978-3-662-45803-7_18","SourcearXiv","Conference: International Symposium on Graph Drawing"],"references":["290989696_Graph_Structure_and_Monadic_Second-Order_Logic_A_Language-Theoretic_Approach","230595900_Embedding_graphs_in_books_A_graph_layout_problem_with_applications_to_VLSI_design","227323894_Some_recent_results_in_topological_graph_theory","226664199_On_the_Parameterized_Complexity_of_Layered_Graph_Drawing","225470294_Crossing_Numbers_and_Parameterized_Complexity","225190786_Recognizing_outerplanar_graphs_in_linear_time","2795827_A_Linear_Time_Algorithm_for_Finding","280982672_On_imbedding_graphs_in_the_plane","277473416_A_Linear-Time_Algorithm_for_Finding_Tree-Decompositions_of_Small_Treewidth","268494086_Planar_permutation_graphs","266924881_On_imbedding_graphs_in_the_sphere","265502171_Fundamentals_of_Parameterized_Complexity","265435677_Graph_minors_XIII_The_disjoint_paths_problem","265351411_Mathematical_logic_Transl_from_the_German_by_Ann_S_Ferebee","256117741_Fixed_Parameter_Tractability_of_Crossing_Minimization_of_Almost-Trees","242601680_Embedding_Graphs_in_Books_A_Layout_Problem_with_Applications_to_VLSI_Design","234814627_Four_pages_are